profile_positions.description:
As a Project Manager in Translational Research (TR), my main tasks are:
- help the TR Leads map and prioritize deliverables for their programs;
​- monitor the progress of the TR team deliverables, capture action items, and follow up with stakeholders to ensure progress;
​- develop overviews of various work packages for TR and Translational Medicine programs​;
​- empower Department Leads and the TR leadership team to make informed decisions on portfolio strategy in a timely manner.
